query_result.query:
SELECT
	 p.message_id AS "activity_id"
	 , p.timestamp AS "ts"
	 , 'segment' AS "source"
	 , p.anonymous_id AS "source_id"
	 , p.user_id AS "customer"
	 , 'marketing_site_page_view' AS "activity"
	 , p.context_page_path AS "feature_1"
	 , nullif ( p.referrer , '' ) AS "feature_2"
	 , NULL  AS "feature_3"
	 , NULL ::FLOAT AS "revenue_impact"
	 , p.context_page_url::varchar ( 250 ) AS "link"
FROM website.pages AS p
limit 1000
